{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/blog-comments-with-giscus/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>블로그에 댓글 기능을 추가하기 위해 구글링을 해보았다.<br>\n예전에는 <a href=\"https://developers.facebook.com/products/social-plugins/comments/\">facebook comments</a> 혹은 <a href=\"https://blog.disqus.com/\">disqus</a>를 사용했던 것 같은데, 접근성이 아쉽거나 관리 비용이 발생한다.<br>\n최근 기술 블로그에서는 GitHub 계정을 기반으로 한 서비스를 많이 사용하는 것으로 보인다.</p>\n<p>GitHub 계정 기반 서비스는 <a href=\"https://utteranc.es/\">utterances</a>가 대표적이고, 최근에는 <a href=\"https://giscus.app/\">giscus</a>도 쓰인다.<br>\n필자는 giscus를 쓰기로 결정했는데, 그 이유는 다음과 같다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>utterances는 repository의 issue를, giscus는 discussion을 기반으로 작동한다.<br>utterances의 경우, 기존 issue들(bug report)과 섞이면 혼잡해지기 때문에 댓글 전용 repository를 따로 둔다.<br>반면 discussion은 카테고리를 나눌 수 있기 때문에 repository를 나눌 필요가 없다.</li>\n<li>상대적으로 theme가 다양하고, 원할 경우 직접 CSS를 작성해서 적용할 수 있다.</li>\n<li>상대적으로 최근까지 활발하게 기능 개발과 유지보수를 진행하고 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>이제 giscus를 적용해보자. <a href=\"https://jojoldu.tistory.com/704\">이 글</a>에서 정보를 얻어 진행했다. 🙏</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>블로그에 giscus 적용하기</h2>\n<h3>GitHub Discussions 활성화</h3>\n<p>먼저, 블로그 Repository의 <code>Settings</code>로 이동하여 <code>Discussions</code> 항목을 활성화한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68.09815950920245%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"discussions_01.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/508467cc34cd25558bf4ddfcf5b5fc48/a6d36/discussions_01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/508467cc34cd25558bf4ddfcf5b5fc48/222b7/discussions_01.png 163w,\n/static/508467cc34cd25558bf4ddfcf5b5fc48/ff46a/discussions_01.png 325w,\n/static/508467cc34cd25558bf4ddfcf5b5fc48/a6d36/discussions_01.png 650w,\n/static/508467cc34cd25558bf4ddfcf5b5fc48/e548f/discussions_01.png 975w,\n/static/508467cc34cd25558bf4ddfcf5b5fc48/3c492/discussions_01.png 1300w,\n/static/508467cc34cd25558bf4ddfcf5b5fc48/92e9f/discussions_01.png 2620w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68.09815950920245%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"discussions_02.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/24bcbd8a38235f7238536ed8cac86215/a6d36/discussions_02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/24bcbd8a38235f7238536ed8cac86215/222b7/discussions_02.png 163w,\n/static/24bcbd8a38235f7238536ed8cac86215/ff46a/discussions_02.png 325w,\n/static/24bcbd8a38235f7238536ed8cac86215/a6d36/discussions_02.png 650w,\n/static/24bcbd8a38235f7238536ed8cac86215/e548f/discussions_02.png 975w,\n/static/24bcbd8a38235f7238536ed8cac86215/3c492/discussions_02.png 1300w,\n/static/24bcbd8a38235f7238536ed8cac86215/92e9f/discussions_02.png 2620w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>카테고리 생성</h3>\n<p>comment들을 모아놓을 전용 카테고리를 생성할 것이다.<br>\n<code>Discussions</code> 탭으로 이동하여 <code>Categories</code> 옆에 있는 펜 모양 버튼을 클릭한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68.09815950920245%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"category_01.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/ca38d4b51b78e1e055c686bded750e05/a6d36/category_01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ca38d4b51b78e1e055c686bded750e05/222b7/category_01.png 163w,\n/static/ca38d4b51b78e1e055c686bded750e05/ff46a/category_01.png 325w,\n/static/ca38d4b51b78e1e055c686bded750e05/a6d36/category_01.png 650w,\n/static/ca38d4b51b78e1e055c686bded750e05/e548f/category_01.png 975w,\n/static/ca38d4b51b78e1e055c686bded750e05/3c492/category_01.png 1300w,\n/static/ca38d4b51b78e1e055c686bded750e05/92e9f/category_01.png 2620w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>우측 <code>New category</code>를 클릭한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68.09815950920245%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"category_02.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/b1a4ef66b8c5d9ddf5b9c173fddfcafb/a6d36/category_02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b1a4ef66b8c5d9ddf5b9c173fddfcafb/222b7/category_02.png 163w,\n/static/b1a4ef66b8c5d9ddf5b9c173fddfcafb/ff46a/category_02.png 325w,\n/static/b1a4ef66b8c5d9ddf5b9c173fddfcafb/a6d36/category_02.png 650w,\n/static/b1a4ef66b8c5d9ddf5b9c173fddfcafb/e548f/category_02.png 975w,\n/static/b1a4ef66b8c5d9ddf5b9c173fddfcafb/3c492/category_02.png 1300w,\n/static/b1a4ef66b8c5d9ddf5b9c173fddfcafb/92e9f/category_02.png 2620w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><code>Category name</code>과 <code>Description</code>을 입력하고, <code>Discussion Format</code>은 <code>Announcement</code>를 선택한다.<br>\n<code>Announcement</code>의 경우 권한이 있는 사람만 discussion을 만들 수 있고, 댓글과 대댓글은 누구나 쓸 수 있다.<br>\n우하단의 <code>Create</code>를 클릭해 생성을 완료한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68.09815950920245%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"category_03.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/21f2606c8d46c461de8ccf4b836c1581/a6d36/category_03.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/21f2606c8d46c461de8ccf4b836c1581/222b7/category_03.png 163w,\n/static/21f2606c8d46c461de8ccf4b836c1581/ff46a/category_03.png 325w,\n/static/21f2606c8d46c461de8ccf4b836c1581/a6d36/category_03.png 650w,\n/static/21f2606c8d46c461de8ccf4b836c1581/e548f/category_03.png 975w,\n/static/21f2606c8d46c461de8ccf4b836c1581/3c492/category_03.png 1300w,\n/static/21f2606c8d46c461de8ccf4b836c1581/92e9f/category_03.png 2620w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>giscus 앱 설치</h3>\n<p>repository에 giscus 앱을 설치한다.<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/apps/giscus\">https://github.com/apps/giscus</a>로 접속해 <code>Install</code>을 클릭한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68.09815950920245%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"giscus_01.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8c27ff3c0b4a0584f23ce23aa1215aaf/a6d36/giscus_01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8c27ff3c0b4a0584f23ce23aa1215aaf/222b7/giscus_01.png 163w,\n/static/8c27ff3c0b4a0584f23ce23aa1215aaf/ff46a/giscus_01.png 325w,\n/static/8c27ff3c0b4a0584f23ce23aa1215aaf/a6d36/giscus_01.png 650w,\n/static/8c27ff3c0b4a0584f23ce23aa1215aaf/e548f/giscus_01.png 975w,\n/static/8c27ff3c0b4a0584f23ce23aa1215aaf/3c492/giscus_01.png 1300w,\n/static/8c27ff3c0b4a0584f23ce23aa1215aaf/92e9f/giscus_01.png 2620w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><code>Only select repositories</code>를 선택하고, 블로그 repository를 추가하여 이 repository에만 접근할 수 있도록 한다.<br>\n하단의 <code>Install</code>을 클릭한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68.09815950920245%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"giscus_02.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/bfa2f26698ab61154b66ca20ed8161ae/a6d36/giscus_02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bfa2f26698ab61154b66ca20ed8161ae/222b7/giscus_02.png 163w,\n/static/bfa2f26698ab61154b66ca20ed8161ae/ff46a/giscus_02.png 325w,\n/static/bfa2f26698ab61154b66ca20ed8161ae/a6d36/giscus_02.png 650w,\n/static/bfa2f26698ab61154b66ca20ed8161ae/e548f/giscus_02.png 975w,\n/static/bfa2f26698ab61154b66ca20ed8161ae/3c492/giscus_02.png 1300w,\n/static/bfa2f26698ab61154b66ca20ed8161ae/92e9f/giscus_02.png 2620w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>script 태그 작성</h3>\n<p>html에 넣을 <code>script</code> 태그를 직접 작성해도 되지만, 공식 가이드의 도움을 받았다.\n<a href=\"https://giscus.app/ko\">https://giscus.app/ko</a>로 접속해 스크롤을 조금 내려서 <code>설정</code> 섹션으로 이동한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68.09815950920245%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"script_01.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/4050ac48d227d46ba08bef5e1bf8a954/a6d36/script_01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4050ac48d227d46ba08bef5e1bf8a954/222b7/script_01.png 163w,\n/static/4050ac48d227d46ba08bef5e1bf8a954/ff46a/script_01.png 325w,\n/static/4050ac48d227d46ba08bef5e1bf8a954/a6